frames.caption: A group of people are gathered outdoors, sharing a meal on woven mats, surrounded by lush greenery. In the background, a wooden house is under construction with workers actively engaged in building activities. The scene captures a harmonious blend of communal dining and collaborative work.
frames.description: The scene is set in a natural, rural environment where a traditional wooden house is being constructed. Workers are seen on scaffolding, while others are seated on the ground, enjoying a meal together. The atmosphere is warm and communal, with a sense of teamwork and shared purpose.

frames.caption: A group of men sit on woven mats enjoying a communal meal in front of a traditional wooden house under construction. The house is elevated on stilts with bamboo scaffolding, and several workers are seen actively building. The scene is set outdoors under a large tree, with dappled sunlight filtering through the leaves.
frames.description: The image depicts a rural setting where a group of men are having a meal together in front of a wooden house being constructed. The setting suggests a communal and collaborative atmosphere, with both dining and construction activities occurring simultaneously.
